WIMS (WWW Interactive Multipurpose Server) is a web server software, designed to implement a full server-side interactivity for scientific and educational applications. It is an open-source software freely downloadable from <a href=http://wims.unice.fr/download/wims/>http://wims.unice.fr/download/wims/</a>.

As a software, it has many unique features:

